window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Is basing one's strategy on dream riddles the best idea?</b></p> <p>Zaena doesn't know what to make of her new friend's prophetic ability, but she's ready to use any tools available to her.</p> <p>Can Zaena's belief in her ultimate success justify the cost of using Saelli's abilities?</p> <p>A critical new clue sends her away from her new home to confront an ancient threat in Europe.</p> <p>Zaena thinks she's ready for whatever might come, but as everyone knows, even a battle-hardened elven princess can be surprised.</p> <p><b>Does anyone really expect a dead tribe to come back to life?</b></p>"; 
